Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.58,0:02:27.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\fs28\shad0}\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N受信賴的時間限制
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:30.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,看來訓練出成果了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.58,0:02:36.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,曹長！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.01,0:02:41.12,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.91,0:02:45.42,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧 曹長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.92,0:02:47.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,托您的福
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.55,0:02:50.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 這種距離的掩護還是頭一次遇到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.05,0:02:52.83,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身手還過得去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.10,0:02:58.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,從哪裏射來的？伍長！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.73,0:03:01.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是山頂的炮台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.40,0:03:03.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,而且射得很準啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:05.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！被瞄準了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:06.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.80,0:03:08.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那些傢伙裏也有耳朵靈敏的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.85,0:03:09.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.30,0:03:13.13,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,隊長 敵人的著彈點迫近了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:15.33,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,看來全體的位置都已被捕捉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.33,0:03:17.32,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 情況不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:20.71,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,小隊 散開後退 再議作戰方案
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:21.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:30.14,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,正面有3個炮台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:35.07,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戰壕佈置了ZAKU 再加上陡峭的山坡...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:36.86,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那條公路是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:42.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那是補給維持方面最重要的公路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:44.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,對聯邦而言是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.15,0:03:49.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那裏還是有辦法過去的 問題是那村子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:53.36,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,被吉翁佔領了很頭痛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:59.22,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,該如何應付那些利用自然地形而成的炮台呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:00.87,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真希望能有支援啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:04.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,等待職員的話 在這邊會被逼入絕境的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.77,0:04:06.99,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 我知道可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:08.94,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:10.24,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是瀑布
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.44,0:04:12.60,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,沿著河繞道去西邊的山坡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:14.86,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,突襲造成混亂的話 或許能行...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:19.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,說得倒輕鬆 那裏是游擊隊出沒的地區
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:20.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,游擊隊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:24.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 誰去奇襲？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.92,0:04:29.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,這瀑布我以前曾去過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:30.79,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,隊長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:32.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,奇襲？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.55,0:04:37.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,反正只是誘敵的話 缺乏經驗的隊長也應該能行的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:40.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,曹長 這裏就交由你來指揮了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.95,0:04:41.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:43.47,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不 這是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.77,0:04:44.92,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你那麼說的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:46.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.35,0:04:49.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,還有時間方面就定3小時吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.08,0:04:53.18,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會在3小時內到達目的地並發動奇襲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:56.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你們從正面牽制敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:56.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:04:59.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,為了以防萬一先申明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:02.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我們進攻敵人等你回應最多只能堅持1小時
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:04.03,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:05.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,曹長以下4人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:09.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,於15時向公路方位前進 待機
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:11.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,等時間一到就發動總攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.15,0:05:12.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:14.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,別被游擊隊什麼的逮住了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:17.12,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,游擊隊也是平民吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:20.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 那些平民才是最可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:23.33,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好 這裏也準備出擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:24.49,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:30.57,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,請多加小心 隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.41,0:05:46.39,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:57.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能會在的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.82,0:06:16.93,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,到底想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:21.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,脫離戰線了呢 少尉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.95,0:06:24.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不知死活的又回來啦 你這個色鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:26.84,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,這幸福的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.69,0:06:29.39,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:32.42,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,幹什麼呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:35.16,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,參觀費啊 上次在瀑布的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.76,0:06:38.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你還沒付吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.05,0:06:40.73,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,連我們都沒看過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:42.86,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,住 住手 誤會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.06,0:06:45.08,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？誤會你什麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.15,0:06:47.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,按住他 我來教訓他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:48.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.85,0:06:49.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.65,0:06:50.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 這是新貨色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.15,0:06:52.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,別弄啦 要是動起來了怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.84,0:06:54.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:07:00.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,停 停下 快停下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:02.93,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 別亂動啊 適可而...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.93,0:07:04.66,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,別亂動的應該是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:16.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是想得到我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.55,0:07:17.78,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.85,0:07:20.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的軍隊都是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.05,0:07:22.87,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,粗魯 下流 骯髒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:24.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你們不也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:25.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:27.64,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你們有資格說別人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:28.64,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,更何況你只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.94,0:07:29.93,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,只是什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.23,0:07:31.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你還只是個小孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.36,0:07:38.14,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那為何那時一直盯著我看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:41.06,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,要說為何... 只是因為很漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.95,0:07:47.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,沒時間和你們糾纏了 讓我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:53.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,BB 戰鬥進入了消耗狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:57.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我們處於極度的緊張感之中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.02,0:08:01.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,拍檔艾歷多亞對聲納寸不離耳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:03.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,偵察著敵人的動靜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:05.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我也在準備著下一次的進攻...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.76,0:08:10.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 這種爛歌也能登上排行榜首
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.85,0:08:11.63,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.93,0:08:14.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,又在寫情書了啦 你也很閒的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:16.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經準備好作戰了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:20.18,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了你會被拋棄的 不要寫了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:20.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,艾歷多亞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:21.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:38.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:39.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.47,0:08:44.19,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,看到你裸體的事我已經道歉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.49,0:08:46.09,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,別作聲快點走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:50.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我說了好幾遍了 沒時間和你們糾纏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:54.01,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也很忙的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.31,0:08:57.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 沒時間了 要把我帶到哪去...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.70,0:09:02.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊！我都說叫你住手了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:17.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,現在去見老大 放規矩點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:19.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！快打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.30,0:09:22.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.24,0:09:29.21,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是BOSS嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.33,0:09:40.68,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,到我的地盤來有何貴幹 西羅·阿瑪達少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.88,0:09:42.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,沒經同意就過來是我不對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.15,0:09:45.24,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在可是在作戰行動中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.05,0:09:46.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:51.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我對你們來說沒什麼用 請放了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.85,0:09:54.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！有在聽我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.50,0:09:57.61,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:09:59.01,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 請快點...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:01.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,請問...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.11,0:10:06.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,失禮了 每天這個時間都有這習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.05,0:10:09.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了 請認真聽我說啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.37,0:10:18.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:20.27,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,艾歷多亞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:22.22,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,上面一片平靜的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.52,0:10:24.94,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,他們該不會是在喝下午茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.24,0:10:28.11,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,曹長 不知道隊長平安到達了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.41,0:10:30.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,他那麼有自信應該沒問題了 上吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:31.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:41.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎樣說 你才能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.75,0:10:44.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你們和聯邦的共同敵人應該是吉翁才對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.25,0:10:50.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,毀掉設在被佔村子裏的炮台對你們沒什麼壞處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.41,0:10:54.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,為了作戰成功 同伴們在等著我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:57.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,把村子從吉翁手上解放出來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.15,0:11:00.72,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你們的同伴也能獲得自由了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.02,0:11:02.89,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託 放我走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.25,0:11:13.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 儘管打過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.41,0:11:18.11,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,隊長...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.42,0:11:25.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,還是放棄了吧 少尉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:29.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:31.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,在老大面前 你想做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:32.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:34.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,他們是我的首批部下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.15,0:11:38.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎能讓還沒來得及熟悉的同伴們因我而陣亡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:39.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,放我走！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.75,0:11:49.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個好傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:51.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,確實確實
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:53.42,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:57.38,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,利用這個傢伙的話不就能把那個村子解放了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:01.94,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那個村子裏有我們的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.35,0:12:05.07,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不如趁此機會把吉翁那些傢伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:06.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那倒也是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:10.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 約定好了 我會解放村子的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:11.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.35,0:12:17.31,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多的病人和傷員很傷腦筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.41,0:12:20.07,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,藥物的話要多少隨便拿 所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.37,0:12:22.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 吉翁那些傢伙真無情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.00,0:12:26.26,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,想要戰利品嗎 行啊 還我自由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:27.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,別得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:33.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但是沒有比軍人的約定更不可靠的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.55,0:12:34.71,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧 琪琪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.01,0:12:36.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這傢伙沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.95,0:12:38.22,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,欠我的債還沒還呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:39.63,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:44.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.35,0:12:48.53,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,別再嘿嘿哈哈地傻笑個不停了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:51.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那好 爸爸 由我來監視他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:55.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,這是當然 不這樣做你也不會聽我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.39,0:12:58.31,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,少尉先生 現在我們休戰如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.95,0:13:03.21,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,揀回條小命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.50,0:13:05.36,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好好答謝小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.46,0:13:08.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琪琪 告訴少尉先生回去的路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.75,0:13:09.21,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.70,0:13:18.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,都成垃圾筒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:20.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,這種時候哪有閒工夫清理這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:26.54,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 毫不抵抗的人都要盡情毆打
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:30.52,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 要去的話就快點進來 沒時間啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:32.84,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.26,0:13:36.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,敢有奇怪的舉動的話 就這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.47,0:13:38.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我能對小孩子做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.78,0:13:40.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我可比你通人情世故得多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:41.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:43.12,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:45.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 把那個還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.25,0:13:48.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是我拿到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:48.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.95,0:13:51.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是借來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:54.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,3點半了！只剩下30分鐘了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:56.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你戴著也不合適呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.57,0:13:57.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:13:58.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫琪琪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:00.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琪琪？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.05,0:14:03.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琪琪·洛基塔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:04.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,快點走吧 西羅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:07.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我西羅... 你...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:09.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我居然被小孩子小看了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:11.17,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,別站在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.98,0:14:16.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要挺住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.55,0:14:18.77,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 有沒有什麼捷徑？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.97,0:14:21.17,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,沿河前進雖然是最快的...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.37,0:14:22.21,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好 就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:23.83,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可是沒有路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:35.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,艾歷多亞 上面有動靜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.99,0:14:37.24,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,現在還聽不出什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:38.72,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,隊長...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:42.88,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,到底要等到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:47.76,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,碰到的話就完蛋了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.96,0:14:48.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:56.76,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢啊 隊長的動靜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:14:58.62,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有 還確認不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.43,0:15:01.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 有客人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:02.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.35,0:15:04.21,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,安靜一點！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.91,0:15:05.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是隊長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:07.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是直升機
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.00,0:15:09.84,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,1架 不 2架！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:16.81,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,還過來？全隊加強對空戒備！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.85,0:15:17.39,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:20.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,饒了我吧 這也是死神招來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.91,0:15:21.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,死神？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.93,0:15:22.63,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,臭名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:27.60,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,諾裏斯大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:32.01,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的部隊很快就會收拾掉那些想爬上來的老鼠們的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.31,0:15:34.27,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,損失了2台ZAKU吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.57,0:15:37.03,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,呃... 請向基尼亞斯閣下說點好話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.13,0:15:40.53,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是在特別視察日發生這種事...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.15,0:15:47.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,他妹妹愛娜小姐聽說非常美麗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.70,0:15:49.07,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不... 失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:55.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 都是因為相信了麻煩的隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.75,0:15:57.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,山達斯 到極限了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.98,0:15:59.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,向公路方位後退！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.75,0:16:00.23,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.53,0:16:01.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,再這樣下去太勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.97,0:16:02.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,曹長！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.88,0:16:14.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,絕不會錯 是隊長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:17.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好 總算開始了 坐穩了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.25,0:16:18.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.82,0:16:25.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 讓我好等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:32.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,隊長真是個無所不能的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:33.73,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,從哪裏來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.03,0:16:36.19,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是從那裏 從河裏發起的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:37.60,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,想夾擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.05,0:16:43.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上放我下去 我用ZAKU出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.38,0:16:48.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了 打中彈藥庫了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:50.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的是少尉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:51.43,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.73,0:16:53.63,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你要下去的話就趁現在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:55.93,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,要給你帶路到最後結束才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.23,0:16:57.14,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,隨便你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:05.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,快點出動！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.35,0:17:19.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊 有2台ZAKU過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.75,0:17:21.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.22,0:17:44.97,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,衝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.43,0:17:48.78,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都來了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.81,0:17:51.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的1台過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.55,0:18:14.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,火箭筒 給我打
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:19.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼!? 連游擊隊都加入了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:22.59,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,陷落只是時間問題了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:25.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,馬撒德 撤退！我來拖延時間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:29.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是 北邊的阻礙請由我來清除
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:32.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣 我去收拾西邊的MS
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.70,0:18:33.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.90,0:18:48.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,艾歷多亞 平民的疏散就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:49.83,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,已經在做了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.13,0:18:50.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.85,0:18:52.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.85,0:18:55.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,游擊隊...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:57.78,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,曹長 能聽到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:18:59.48,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:02.28,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起我來晚了 大家都沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.58,0:19:03.28,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:06.79,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,解放村子 特別注意別傷到平民
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.59,0:19:08.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.15,0:19:10.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,軍曹 聽到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:12.17,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.54,0:19:16.11,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:30.44,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,聯邦和游擊隊的協同作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:36.52,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.71,0:20:03.53,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,這個敵人有點本事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.83,0:20:05.03,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 到此為止了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.34,0:20:09.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:11.14,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道... 可沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:23.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,閉上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.70,0:20:35.47,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.72,0:20:47.79,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,收拾掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:48.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.05,0:20:58.60,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,居然有擅長水中戰的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.51,0:21:03.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧 在那裏 要逃掉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.95,0:21:05.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:07.49,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,現在這個狀態是無法縱深追擊的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.50,0:21:10.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,明明差一點就逮到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.45,0:21:16.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真是大豐收
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:19.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的收穫真不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.57,0:21:20.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,為所欲為啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.25,0:21:22.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那是理所當然的權利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.98,0:21:25.23,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了 你們還真是活躍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.22,0:21:35.56,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是無情的傢伙們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.86,0:21:37.03,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.33,0:21:40.07,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是我們解放了這個村子的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.37,0:21:42.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 再稍微感謝一下也好...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.45,0:21:48.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,幹什麼... 你們想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.35,0:21:52.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡透了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.55,0:21:54.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好 這槍還真猛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.95,0:21:56.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 誰帶了扳手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.58,0:21:58.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.28,0:22:03.12,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,俘虜運送的車輛準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.22,0:22:03.86,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.16,0:22:05.99,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可這種光景...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.29,0:22:08.63,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼也得約束一下這些傢伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.93,0:22:12.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,約定好了的 讓他們隨便拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.70,0:22:14.68,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係吧 約書亞曹長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.88,0:22:15.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.10,0:22:17.77,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不 叫我卡蓮就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:21.09,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我遲到了 對不起 卡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.39,0:22:22.09,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.32,0:22:27.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,西羅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.50,0:22:29.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.55,0:22:31.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,女朋友？懷表的主人
